OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with patchy rain
OL,6,Fclearing during the morning for
OL,7,FOrkney, through the afternoon for
OL,8,FShetland. Otherwise a bright day with
OL,9,Fsunny spells and a few showers. Strong
OL,10,Fwinds, occasional gales for Shetland
OL,11,Faround early afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMostly dry to start with
OL,14,Fsunny spells and just the odd shower.
OL,15,FTurning somewhat cloudier overnight
OL,16,Fwith a few showers but still some dry,
OL,17,Fclear spells. Strong winds will ease.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
