OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,6,Fvariable cloud throughout the day.
OL,7,FMostly dry but the odd light shower
OL,8,Fpossible. Winds freshen in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Fchangeable westerly pattern brings
OL,13,Fvariable cloud and scattered showers
OL,14,Fduring this period, with some sunshine
OL,15,Fat times but often windy.
